meta.expressionLhs: CASE WHEN ISNULL ( ABC ( PU_SUM ( "LFA1" , PU_SUM ( "EKKO" , "EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED" ) ) , 0.8 , 0.15 ) ) = 1 THEN 'Vendor with no order' WHEN ABC ( PU_SUM ( "LFA1" , PU_SUM ( "EKKO" , "EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED" ) ) , 0.8 , 0.15 ) = 1 THEN 'A' WHEN ABC ( PU_SUM ( "LFA1" , PU_SUM ( "EKKO" , "EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED" ) ) , 0.8 , 0.15 ) = 2 THEN 'B' ELSE 'C' END AS "ABC"

axis0.name: ABC
axis0.text:
CASE
  WHEN  ISNULL(ABC(PU_SUM("LFA1", PU_SUM("EKKO", "EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED"))  , <%= ABC_upper_limit %>, <%= ABC_lower_limit %>)) = 1
  THEN 'Vendor with no order'
  
  WHEN ABC(PU_SUM("LFA1", PU_SUM("EKKO", "EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED"))  , <%= ABC_upper_limit %>, <%= ABC_lower_limit %>) = 1
  THEN 'A'

  WHEN ABC(PU_SUM("LFA1", PU_SUM("EKKO", "EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED"))  , <%= ABC_upper_limit %>, <%= ABC_lower_limit %>) = 2
  THEN 'B'
  
  ELSE 'C'
END

variables.name: ButtonDrilldown4
variables.value: CASE WHEN PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") >= 0 AND PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") <= 100 THEN 'a) 0 - 100€' WHEN PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") > 100 AND PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") <= 500 THEN 'b) 100 - 500€' WHEN PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") > 500 AND PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") <= 1000 THEN 'c) 500 - 1.000€' WHEN PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") > 1000 AND PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") <= 10000 THEN 'd) 1.000 - 10.000€' ELSE 'e) > 10.000€' END
